<figureCitation box="[724,788,1653,1676]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 5" captionStartId="1.[151,264,1769,1792]" captionTargetBox="[192,1417,471,1709]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[151,1436,435,1748]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 5. Aeolothrips eremicola male (1) Antennae; (2) Tergites III – VI; (3) Tergites IX – X. A. eremicola female (4) Hind leg; (5) Sternites VI – VII." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/220703/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="289">
